            .(The case was opened by Mr. Gurney.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18010701-34-person336">
                  JOHN 
                  HOPWOOD
               <interp inst="t18010701-34-person336" type="surname" value="HOPWOOD"></interp>
